</span></p><ul style="--pf-line-spacing-xs:10px;--pf-line-spacing-sm:10px;--pf-line-spacing-md:10px;--pf-line-spacing-lg:10px;--pf-text-indent-xs:0px;--pf-text-indent-sm:0px;--pf-text-indent-md:0px;--pf-text-indent-lg:0px" data-pf-type="List2" class="sc-eifsgl epDHtf pf-198_"><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-fKWLGC lflwGM pf-199_">What do we actually need today?
</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-fKWLGC lflwGM pf-201_">Have we truly tested this system?
</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-fKWLGC lflwGM pf-203_">Will it adapt if we grow or restructure?
</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-fKWLGC lflwGM pf-205_">What happens if we want to exit?
</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-fKWLGC lflwGM pf-207_">Who will support us long after we make the purchase?
</li></ul><p class="sc-EROOM ZMPII pf-209_" data-pf-type="Paragraph4"><input type="checkbox" id="compact-3b832098-68f8-42e2-917a-c48834c470dd"/><span class="pf-paragraph-content ">These five questions can save time, reduce stress, and support safer, more effective care delivery.
</span></p></div></div></div><div class="sc-hzhKNl fltMam pf-212_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-bkSTSn hpQOMO pf-213_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-kRRxPL kSaugo pf-214_">Final word - Clarity beats complexity
